# Simple example schedule for RailOCS.
# We have GpusPerServer=8 => 8 ToRs (rails) indexed 0..7.
# Planes=4 => plane ids 0..3.
#
# Format:
#   slot <slot_id>
#     plane <p> <tor_a>-<tor_b> <tor_c>-<tor_d> ...
#
# Within each plane, ToRs should appear at most once (a matching).
#
# This example connects (0<->1, 2<->3, 4<->5, 6<->7) on all planes for slot 0.

slot 0
plane 0 0-1 2-3 4-5 6-7
plane 1 0-1 2-3 4-5 6-7
plane 2 0-1 2-3 4-5 6-7
plane 3 0-1 2-3 4-5 6-7


